{"tid":1833674,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：中央加強對香港控制指控沒有道理","createTime":"2020-01-22T04:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T06:40:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9051de8bca318c6e74b2b135473182b111e669e7","tid":1833674,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20200122_20200122-105736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20200122_20200122-105736.jpg&h=4dd373e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20200122_20200122-094826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20200122_20200122-094826.jpg&h=2a1200f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正在瑞士達沃斯出席世界經濟論壇年會的行政長官林鄭月娥，接受彭博社訪問時指，中央政府加強對香港控制的指控沒有道理，強調中央明確表示，希望香港在一國兩制和高度自治下取得成功，國家主席習近平近幾個月三次與她見面，亦都清楚表達。<br />\n<br />\n她重申不會辭職，會竭盡所能控制當前局勢，又指香港要清楚了解優勢所在，認為本港金融服務在過去一年表現好，今年表現應不錯，強調香港是中國連接外國的橋樑。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥接受美國財經頻道CNBC訪問時對評級機構穆迪下調香港主權信貸評級感到非常失望，亦不認同穆迪指香港的管治能力薄弱，她說，經過七個月的社會動盪，已證明香港的體制及治理具有韌性，又指美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》毫無必要。"},{"pid":"cd4b8fd5218cde428eb456fe0fe4b215caefe886","tid":1833674,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:14:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1254818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1254818&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=2ee7361e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1254818</a>"},{"pid":"a50fc2550eaefc16ff45d6dd388a01c3b5a5546f","tid":1833674,"uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"鬼佬訪問佢把批咩"},{"pid":"091557a0df83c2c1ec9ca7a2